ct(fields))\n            .map(Some)\n            .map_err(Into::into)\n    }\n\n    /// Remove a metadata key.\n    ///\n    /// Uses the session's email and timestamp automatically.\n    pub fn remove(&self, key: &str) -> Result<bool> {\n","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-10T20:42:26.636Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"[REDACTED:entropy]"}}}